{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they'd help themselves off the Germans, kind of thing, whatever they fancied.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they looked at my raw potatoes and greens and, and thought I was mad and I was an idiot, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said I would do better next day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And on the next day, then, I was very lucky, because I found the nearby cheese factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I also found a wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So in the evening, I came back with a wheelbarrow full of tubes of cheese.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were making tubes of cheese there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I had a wheelbarrow full of tubes of cheese, and I thought I had done very well that day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when all the others came back from Trebitz, they'd been in the cellars of the German houses, and they came back with food-- fruit and preserves and gateaus.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and they'd-- off the Germans, they'd taken their watches, and they came back with radios and bicycles and some of them with cars.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And some of them had actually turfed the Germans out of their houses and taken over the German houses in Trebitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So me with my wheelbarrow of tubes of cheese-- everybody thought I was an idiot again, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I obviously hadn't caught on to the new situation at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [NON-ENGLISH] was well to the forefront, and he'd done very well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He'd got a motorbike, a thing which he proudly brought back to the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then everybody else started to move into the village of Trebitz and turfing the Germans out of their houses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just wasn't up to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, I was actually very ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had-- my legs had swollen tremendously, and I, I couldn't walk very well.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
